Package: trimbosR
Title: trimbosR: Toolbox for analyses at Trimbos-instituut.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Ben", "Wijnen", , "bwijnen@trimbos.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: trimbosR is an internally developed R package designed to streamline and standardize commonly used statistical workflows at the Trimbos‑instituut. The package bundles frequently applied functions, data wrangling shortcuts, and analytical utilities into a single, easy‑to‑use toolkit..
